result.name: Green Common

reviews.text:
I love Green Common and was so happy to see the big sign in QRE Plaza. It is located in a great spot. The food was a little salty but delicious. I am vegetarian so was tempted to buy up all the cool vegetarian snacks, food, and meals. The only reason for not 5 star was when I was trying to order my food at the counter there was a worker who was finishing her shift and was buying some products. The two other people behind the counter kind of ignored me and was not very warmly to take my order.

I feel like a bowl of noodles (with an upgrade) and added drink for 103 was not too bad.

I absolutely love this place! All the food is delicious! The breakfast with The Beyond sausage and JUST egg is amazing, the mushroom, truffle sauce and vegan cheese pizza is to die for and the Beyond burger is epic. One of the many ethical businesses making a difference ❤
Great food. Really amazing burgers that are delicious and sustainable. There’s also a grocery section in case you want to get stock up for home. Nice low key service as well.

Recommended by a friend who works nearby. A go green restaurant. All vegan.
Ordered a curry plant-based burger rice recommended by the staff, it is nice and decent for this place. Quite a big menu including burgers, mains, desserts and snacks. Will come again definitely. Feel healthy after the meal.
Food: 5/5
Price: 5/5
Environment: 3/5 (seating area is not extremely good and the music at the background can be quite annoying sometimes.....)
Staff: 3/5 (not very helpful and sometimes can overhear what staff say....)

Overall: 4/5
Will recommend people who like healthy and vegan diet. For people who want something light, a good choice for you.
I love Green Common. It makes live of a vegan so much easier! There is a cafe with sitting and a shop. Food arrived in just two minutes!
